rComments: Chakraborty is very bad at explaining things, doesn't have a very coherent lecture scheme and jumps through all his lectures slides too quickly to understand what he is talking about, much less take notes.  I wouldn't reccommend taking a class taught by him.

Dr. Chakraborty could barely speak English. I guarantee that if you take his course you will regret it. When the professor went on vacation for a week, his T.A. took over and people actually began coming to lecture because the explanation of concepts and basic articulation was ten times better. And dont even try to get the A when you have an 89.9%
